The Bank of England said it had providedthe money market with 16 mln stg help in the afternoon session.    The Bank did not operate in the market in the morning andearlier revised its estimate of the shortage in the systemtoday down to 400 mln stg from 450 mln.    The central bank purchased bills outright in band one at10-3/8 pct comprising two mln stg of local authority bills and14 mln stg of bank bills. REUTER&#3;